of champagne.

04:18.724 --> 04:20.021
Better ask to get traded.

04:20.226 --> 04:23.593
You gotta give the Yankees...

04:23.796 --> 04:25.388
win the big game.

04:25.598 --> 04:29.364
What a series that is gonna be
in the next...

