05:05.671 --> 05:09.038
It's like we're a farm system
for the New York Yankees.

05:14.847 --> 05:17.315
- How are the guys doing?
- That was a killer.

05:17.516 --> 05:20.451
That was a killer.
It's a tough one to swallow. It's...

05:20.653 --> 05:23.213
- They played great.
- They played their hearts out.

05:23.422 --> 05:26.619
They did. They played fantastic.
It just didn't fall our way.

05:26.826 --> 05:29.727
- You'll do better next year.
- But we were close, though.

05:29.929 --> 05:31.920
- We were so close.
- Right there.

05:32.131 --> 05:34.497
Almost had it.
You gotta feel good about that.

05:34.700 --> 05:37.897
I feel great about it.
I feel great about it.

05:42.675 --> 05:44.939
We're not gonna do better next year.

05:45.144 --> 05:48.011
- Why not?
- Well, you know we're being gutted.

05:48.214 --> 05:53.151
We're losing Giambi,
